y, from pre-COVID.  We got a short cruise to try it out (ehhhhh….)

We were eating dinner in the main dining room, and were having a fine time, until an older couple started giving us really bad looks.

My wife is usually concerned bad looks mean someone isn’t ok with us (interracial).  Usually I’m an optimist, but these people were straight up STARING.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/itNCNa7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>In the middle of eating one of them throws down their silverware and marches over, followed by the other.  Once they get all the way to us we just stared at each other for about 3 or 4 seconds before the wife says “oh my god you aren’t our grandson”

Apparently I was doppelgänger close in appearance, and their grandson was away on a supposed business trip while leaving his pregnant wife at home.  They straight up thought they had caught him cheating with some girl on a cruise on accident!

They apologized and laughed with us for a minute, but we were 100% sure we were about to have a viral moment.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/omyCNMc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[willCodeForUpvotes]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When you fucking nail the photo shoot.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ri9XeSH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tdcq43g.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fun stuff…send something fucking great.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ri9XeSH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[deafkitten]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Awesome Dad</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cQ15Jie</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qZZxLa2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.india.com/viral/father-of-the-year-this-afghan-man-travels-12-km-every-day-to-take-his-daughters-to-school-3870234/

