some Googling, and learned that when rabbits eat the bark of buckthorn, the phytochemicals that come out in their urine turn blue after being exposed to the sun! 

We have a big ol momma bun that hangs out around our yard year-round, and on closer inspection there is bunny poop around all the blue areas, so this is definitely her doing. Sure startled me, though!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LP99X4x.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bun tax, not my photo because I haven’t managed to get one of her yet.

Sauce that satisfied my curiosity: http://blog.adventurepublications.net/2020/02/blue-spots-in-the-snow-could-it-be-the-cottontail-rabbit/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/G6UkCrq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Shloobs]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Henry cavil</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FxdEWNA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iRoc79t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/FxdEWNA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Swiggetyspaggetie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sweetness</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/o7IL3Wz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h0bMEoc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/o7IL3Wz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>the best 13th favorite</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/P8TtoIK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pF03rEU.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QAhNCtt.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f5vl2cG.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/APeSr18.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oxNmw9M.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nIdwFVw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Edit: holy hell you guys really like debating snails thank you so much for the love!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/P8TtoIK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WinnTheWise]]></dc:creator><